text: Ceroplesis aethiopica is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1974. It is known from Ethiopia.BioLib.cz - Ceroplesis aethiopica. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Ceroplesis Category:Beetles described in 1974
